name: Ryobi Jet Fan Cordless Blower - Gas-Like Power, 155mph
description: The unique jet fan design of the Ryobi cordless blower optimizes air flow to produce Gas-Like Power at 155 mph and 300 CFM. The cordless jet fan blower blasts through wet and dry leaves and debris and is ideal for lawns and hard surfaces. Other product features include a variable speed trigger for air speed control and an overall sleek design with a soft grip handle for user comfort. It starts quickly and easily, without the hassle of gas and oil.
